{"title_page": "The Knock", "text_new": "{{other uses}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2016}}\n{{Use British English|date=October 2016}}\n{{Infobox television\n |show_name          = The Knock\n |show_name_2        = \n |image              = Theknocktvseries.jpg\n |image_upright      =\n |caption            = <small>(L to R: The show's main cast in Series Two \u2014 Marston Bloom, Enzo Squillino Jr., Steve Toussaint, Caroline Lee Johnson, Malcolm Storry, Alex Kingston, Andrew Dunn and Tracey Whitwell.)</small>\n |creator            = Anita Bronson\n |genre              = [[Crime fiction|Crime drama]]\n |writer             = Anita Bronson<br>Geoffrey Case<br>[[Ian Kennedy Martin]]<br>Steve Trafford<br>Stephen Leather\n |director           = Various\n |editor             = Nigel Parkes\n |starring           = [[Caroline Lee-Johnson]]<br>[[Steve Toussaint]]<br>[[Enzo Squillino, Jr.]]<br>[[Malcolm Storry]]<br>Marston Bloom<br>[[Andrew Dunn (actor)|Andrew Dunn]]<br>[[Mark Lewis Jones]]<br>[[Peter O'Brien (actor)|Peter O'Brien]]<br>[[Alex Kingston]]<br>Tracey Whitwell<br>Daniel O'Grady<br>Daniel Brown<br>Sarah Malin<br>[[Jonathan Kerrigan]]<br>[[Michelle Morris]]<br>[[Zig Byfield]]\n |composer           = [[Brian Bennett]]<br>[[Warren Bennett (musician)|Warren Bennett]]\n |opentheme          = \n |endtheme           = \"The Knock\"\n |country            = {{Unbulleted list|United Kingdom}}\n |language           = {{Unbulleted list|English}}\n |num_series         = 5\n |num_episodes       = 37\n |list_episodes      = #Episodes\n |executive_producer = Paul Knight\n |producer           = Phillip Leach\n |location           = {{Unbulleted list|United Kingdom}}\n |runtime            = 75 minutes <br><small>(w/advertisements) (Series 1-4)</small> <br> 105 minutes <small>(w/advertisements) (Series 5)</small>\n |company            = Bronson/Knight Productions for [[London Weekend Television|LWT]]\n |channel            = {{Unbulleted list|[[ITV (TV network)|ITV]]}}\n |picture_format     = [[4:3]] <small>(1994\u201397)</small><br>[[16:9]] <small>(1999\u20132000)</small>\n |audio_format        = [[Monaural|Mono]] <small>(1994\u201396)</small><br>[[Stereophonic sound|Stereo]] <small>(1997\u20132000)</small>\n |first_aired        = {{start date|1994|4|10|df=yes}}\n |last_aired         = {{end date|2000|11|11|df=yes}}\n}}\n\n'''''The Knock''''' is a [[Television in the United Kingdom|British]] television [[crime drama]], created by Anita Bronson and broadcast on [[ITV (TV network)|ITV]], which portrayed the activities of [[customs]] officers from the London City & South Collection Investigation Unit of [[HM Customs and Excise]].<ref>http://www.tv.com/shows/the-knock/episodes/</ref> The series derived its name from the distinctive \"''Knock knock knock''\" command used over the radio to synchronise a raid.\n\nFive series were broadcast from 10 April 1994, until 11 November 2000. The series had a rotating cast, with only a small number of cast members appearing throughout the series' run. The only three cast members to appear in every series were [[Caroline Lee-Johnson]], [[Trevor Byfield]] and [[Steve Toussaint]]. The series also adopted a number of different formats: while the early series interspersed various storylines and had running plots across the series; later series adopted a multi-part format resulting in two or three cases per series; while the final series adopted a stand-alone week by-week format.\n\nThe series was axed in 2001 following poor viewing figures for the final series. This was blamed on the loss of several main cast members, a change in the format and the overall look of the series which changed dramatically following an overhaul by ITV executives in 1999.<ref>http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/27-april-2001/846.issue</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n\n===Main cast===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10%;\"| Character\n! colspan=5| Series\n|-\n! style=\"width:8%;\"| Series 1\n! style=\"width:8%;\"| Series 2\n! style=\